{
  "stem": "1721.1",
  "chunk_idx": 11,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 12.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "I think I remember being on top of a little hill, on top of a knoll, and just sort of looking down at the barracks.",
      "word_count": 25
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Theresienstadt was a-- it was a sort of, like it was a barracks.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "It was a soldiers' barracks at one time, like a garrison.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So it had barracks, and it had administrative buildings.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And then of course, it had some open spaces-- green spaces they call them today.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And so I was able to-- I would not go into buildings, but I would just-- I don't recall exactly.",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 55,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "I just remember just, you know, exploring a lot on my own.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "Probably.",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "But I don't remember being treated harshly personally, as far as physical harm.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I remember we didn't very much.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "We had barley soup.",
      "word_count": 4
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "I was raised on barley soup, and I love barley soup today.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "I just was-- that's all.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "Barley soup, 20 times a day.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Well, one time a day, I guess.",
      "word_count": 7
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "It's not very much else.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "Couple of instances, things I remember, I know that they used to bring a food supply into the camp on some of the trains.",
      "word_count": 24
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "And we used to-- a few times, we would sneak out in the middle the night.",
      "word_count": 16
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "In the dark of night-- kids-- and we would find our way to the railroads.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "And we would crawl underneath the railroad cars and look for small potatoes that used to fall in between the cracks.",
      "word_count": 21
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "If they were small enough, they would fall between the cracks.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 14,
      "text": "And so we would gather up some potatoes and bring it back to the barracks with us.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And we would slice them up.",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "And we would lay them out on top of the stove.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 56,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "We had our own way of making french fries, I guess.",
      "word_count": 11
    }
  ],
